# How to submit manually!
When submitting please follow this format, or something similar:

```
Image: example.png
Artist: u/example (twitter)

Image: example2.jpg
Artist: u/example2 (reddit)
```

***Please be aware since you are submitting manually it might take me a bit to implement your contribution (" o.o)***
